            "content_html": "<main>\n    <p>\n\tSummary of BCD changes from <a href=\"\"><time title=\"Monday, 15 June 2026\">Monday, 15 June 2026</time></a> through <time title=\"Monday, 22 June 2026\">Monday, 22 June 2026</time></strong><a href=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/weekly-completed/2026-06-22.html\" title=\"permalink\">🔗</a>\n    </p>\n    <hr>\n\n\n          <p class=\"callout\"><strong>49 new universal implementations</strong></p>\n          <section class=\"added implementations\">\n\t            <h4>API</h4>\n              <ol>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/RTCInboundRtpStreamStats/transportId\">api ➞ RTCStatsReport ➞ type_inbound-rtp ➞ transportId</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/RTCOutboundRtpStreamStats/transportId\">api ➞ RTCStatsReport ➞ type_outbound-rtp ➞ transportId</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/RTCRemoteInboundRtpStreamStats/transportId\">api ➞ RTCStatsReport ➞ type_remote-inbound-rtp ➞ transportId</a>\n                      </span>\n    