            "content_html": "<main>\n    <p>\n\tSummary of BCD changes from <a href=\"\"><time title=\"Monday, 18 May 2026\">Monday, 18 May 2026</time></a> through <time title=\"Monday, 25 May 2026\">Monday, 25 May 2026</time></strong><a href=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/weekly-completed/2026-05-25.html\" title=\"permalink\">🔗</a>\n    </p>\n    <hr>\n\n\n          <p class=\"callout\"><strong>8 new universal implementations</strong></p>\n          <section class=\"added implementations\">\n\t            <h4>API</h4>\n              <ol>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/Element/requestPointerLock#unadjustedmovement\">api ➞ Element ➞ requestPointerLock ➞ options_unadjustedMovement_parameter</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>api ➞ MathMLElement ➞ nonce\n                      \t<a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/urls-and-fetching.html#dom-noncedelement-nonce\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg\" alt=\"Spec link\"></a>\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/finalResponseHeadersStart\">api ➞ PerformanceResourceTiming ➞ finalResponseHeadersStart</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/firstInterimResponseStart\">api ➞ PerformanceResourceTiming ➞ firstInterimResponseStart</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>api ➞ RTCPeerConnection ➞ RTCPeerConnection ➞ configuration_rtcpMuxPolicy_parameter\n                      \t<a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webrtc-pc/#dom-rtcconfiguration-rtcpmuxpolicy\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg\" alt=\"Spec link\"></a>\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n              </ol>\n\t            <h4>CSS</h4>\n              <ol>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/CSS/Reference/Properties/field-sizing\">css ➞ properties ➞ field-sizing</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>css ➞ properties ➞ field-sizing ➞ content\n                      \t<a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-forms-1/#valdef-field-sizing-content\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg\" alt=\"Spec link\"></a>\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>css ➞ properties ➞ field-sizing ➞ fixed\n                      \t<a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-forms-1/#valdef-field-sizing-fixed\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg\" alt=\"Spec link\"></a>\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n              </ol>\n          </section>\n\n  <hr>\n  <ul id=\"prev-next\">\n  \t<li>Previous report: <a href=\"\"><time title=\"Monday, 18 May 2026\">Monday, 18 May 2026</time></a></li>\n  </ul>\n  <hr>\n  <footer>\n  \t<p>\n  \t<a href=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/\">BCD Watch</a>: A service of <a href=\"https://igalia.com\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/igalia-logo.png\" alt=\"Igalia\"></a>\n  \t</p>\n  \t<p>\n  \tSubscribe: <a href=\"feed.rss\">RSS</a> • <a href=\"feed.atom\">Atom</a> • <a href=\"feed.json\">JSON</a>\n  \t</p>\n\t\t<div class=\"subfooter\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"details\">\n\t\t\tThis report was generated by diffing <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data/releases/tag/v7.3.16\">v7.3.16</a> <small>(Friday, 15 May 2026)</small> and <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data/releases/tag/v8.0.0\">v8.0.0</a> <small>(Friday, 22 May 2026)</small>\n\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t</div>\n  </footer>\n  </main>",
